DDR-3 AI Basic (Task)
DDR-3 AI Flight (Move)
DDR-3 AI Offensive (Combat)
DDR-3 AI Recorder (Land)
DDR-3 AI Recorder (Launch)
DDR-3 Antenna
DDR-3 Corner Light
DDR-3 Event Controller
DDR-3 Gatling Gun
DDR-3 Offset Light
DDR-3 Gyroscope
DDR-3 Thrusters
DDR-3 Connector
DDR-3 Program [EA2]
DDR-3 Debug LCD
DDR-3 Timer
DDR-3 Battery

@Launch
{
    Discharge DDR-3 Battery
    OnOff_On DDR-3 Thruster
    OnOff_On DDR-3 Gyroscope
    Writenew to DDR-3 Debug LCD = Flight Systems up
    Delay 3000
    OnOff_On DDR-3 Corner Light
    OnOff_On DDR-3 Offset Light
    Writeline to DDR-3 Debug LCD = Light Systems up
    Delay 3000
    OnOff_On DDR-3 Antenna
    Writeline to DDR-3 Debug LCD = Comm Systems up
    Delay 3000
    Writeline to DDR-3 Debug LCD = Releasing Drone
    Delay 3000
    Unlock DDR-3 Connector
}

@Land
{
    Delay 3000
    OnOff_Off DDR-3 Thruster
    Delay 3000
    When connected of DDR-3 Connector = Connectable 
    {
        Lock DDR-3 Connector
        Recharge DDR-3 Battery
        OnOff_Off DDR-3 Gyroscope
        OnOff_Off DDR-3 Corner Light
        OnOff_Off DDR-3 Offset Light
        OnOff_Off DDR-3 Antenna
    }
}